  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a molcajete over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic, ginger, cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the rest-meat and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the fregola, water, lemon juice, and honey. Bring to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the parsley, cilantro, and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!",
    "Garnish with additional parsley and cilantro, if desired."
